{"tid":2264482,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[電學工程入]想請教有關supercap嘅問題","createTime":"2020-10-30T16:08:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T17:54:43.000Z","uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da82aae0658641d6581397c1eb0f29cdb5b987a2","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:08:47.000Z","msg":"小弟非engine中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過近排有需要用到supercap又唔識就上嚟問下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講下背景先,之前有玩過supercap,不過唔係我操刀,所以都只係大約知做緊咩<br />\n所以我嚟緊嘅問題會base on之前個電路嚟問<br />\n大約係咁:<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oaSzkwv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoaSzkwv.png&h=a19dcfc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入面啲cap全部2.7v<br />\n叉電係用塊12v嘅太陽能板,會output~0.2A<br />\n啲cap係推3v tamiya嘅摩打<br />\n<br />\n1.想問下照呢個case換cap,高電壓定高電容好?係無分別定係有唔同用途?例如低電壓高電容會叉快啲同多啲電?<br />\n2.點解我計完成個電壓係~4v,但係又可以叉到5-6v?去到6點幾v先爆cap?<br />\n3.之前聽講過電容個電壓要同唔知咩電壓要差唔多先會叉得最有效率係指乜野?<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁多先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"5089e728970cd0a8c0af76b836b67fb3e9a7271e","tid":2264482,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:17:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe6881d47090d9bce474b73ec02d269ce6fbf7ed","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為太陽能板電壓12v<br />\n12/3=4V <br />\n每一個你會有4v<br />\n而xap上面寫的是rated voltage<br />\n超過這個就有可能爆<br />\n<br />\n而太陽能板其實可以去到20v<br />\nthis case is easy to solve<br />\npls parallel a 300k resistance and a 12v zenar diode<br />\nalso please parallel 5-6 cap in one string."},{"pid":"54006c987707eacd325100b8bcbc7c132720690a","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe6881d47090d9bce474b73ec02d269ce6fbf7ed","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為太陽能板電壓12v<br />\n12/3=4V <br />\n每一個你會有4v<br />\n而xap上面寫的是rated voltage<br />\n超過這個就有可能爆<br />\n<br />\n而太陽能板其實可以去到20v<br />\nthis case is easy to solve<br />\npls parallel a 300k resistance and a 12v zenar diode<br />\nalso please parallel 5-6 cap in one string."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"also for each capacitor you can parallel a 3v zenar diode."},{"pid":"d22316ab967b5061d1417d020e8929b9680559fb","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe6881d47090d9bce474b73ec02d269ce6fbf7ed","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為太陽能板電壓12v<br />\n12/3=4V <br />\n每一個你會有4v<br />\n而xap上面寫的是rated voltage<br />\n超過這個就有可能爆<br />\n<br />\n而太陽能板其實可以去到20v<br />\nthis case is easy to solve<br />\npls parallel a 300k resistance and a 12v zenar diode<br />\nalso please parallel 5-6 cap in one string."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />get唔到12/3=4個位<br />\n我係指6個cap當做一個cap睇係~4v(希望我無計錯啦)<br />\n正常電池嚟講應該係叉到額定電壓就等於充滿左<br />\n但係啲cap又可以over charge<br />\n係唔係代表其實我可以無視製造商比嘅電壓用返cap最大可以充嘅電壓即係rated voltage?<br />\n<br />\n至於啲英文我真係唔知up緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟唔係讀engine的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a8ecd5535e70eb73997084a232aef50a8b2b5f","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22316ab967b5061d1417d020e8929b9680559fb","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe6881d47090d9bce474b73ec02d269ce6fbf7ed","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為太陽能板電壓12v<br />\n12/3=4V <br />\n每一個你會有4v<br />\n而xap上面寫的是rated voltage<br />\n超過這個就有可能爆<br />\n<br />\n而太陽能板其實可以去到20v<br />\nthis case is easy to solve<br />\npls parallel a 300k resistance and a 12v zenar diode<br />\nalso please parallel 5-6 cap in one string."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />get唔到12/3=4個位<br />\n我係指6個cap當做一個cap睇係~4v(希望我無計錯啦)<br />\n正常電池嚟講應該係叉到額定電壓就等於充滿左<br />\n但係啲cap又可以over charge<br />\n係唔係代表其實我可以無視製造商比嘅電壓用返cap最大可以充嘅電壓即係rated voltage?<br />\n<br />\n至於啲英文我真係唔知up緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟唔係讀engine的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"電池都會過充<br />\n所以會有過壓保護<br />\n鋰電（磷酸鐵鋰除外）過4.2就會危險著火爆炸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太陽能板係一個電流源<br />\n它本身由太陽能電池組成。<br />\n你那個它可以提供從1v到20v的電壓<br />\n因此實際可以提供超過12v電壓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此你需要串聯至少5個2.7v cap當一條電池。<br />\n最簡單的保護方式是並聯一個12v齊納二極管。這個當時並不十分穩固，可以話係，只堪一用。而且買齊納二極管需要注意額定值達到4w比較好。"},{"pid":"f0473b5c1105de4de4b109566ed961070945f8d9","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:56:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EJ3Ciz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEJ3Ciz9.png&h=940b676a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n像這種比較合適"},{"pid":"260c30237340855538136a77d195060ade039d39","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"最好再並聯一個0.25瓦 的100k歐姆電阻都會是比較理想的做法"},{"pid":"3bf33d4cdb9c58463acf852201edff5c0309e031","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a8ecd5535e70eb73997084a232aef50a8b2b5f","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d22316ab967b5061d1417d020e8929b9680559fb","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe6881d47090d9bce474b73ec02d269ce6fbf7ed","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"因為太陽能板電壓12v<br />\n12/3=4V <br />\n每一個你會有4v<br />\n而xap上面寫的是rated voltage<br />\n超過這個就有可能爆<br />\n<br />\n而太陽能板其實可以去到20v<br />\nthis case is easy to solve<br />\npls parallel a 300k resistance and a 12v zenar diode<br />\nalso please parallel 5-6 cap in one string."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:35:42.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />get唔到12/3=4個位<br />\n我係指6個cap當做一個cap睇係~4v(希望我無計錯啦)<br />\n正常電池嚟講應該係叉到額定電壓就等於充滿左<br />\n但係啲cap又可以over charge<br />\n係唔係代表其實我可以無視製造商比嘅電壓用返cap最大可以充嘅電壓即係rated voltage?<br />\n<br />\n至於啲英文我真係唔知up緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟唔係讀engine的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"電池都會過充<br />\n所以會有過壓保護<br />\n鋰電（磷酸鐵鋰除外）過4.2就會危險著火爆炸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太陽能板係一個電流源<br />\n它本身由太陽能電池組成。<br />\n你那個它可以提供從1v到20v的電壓<br />\n因此實際可以提供超過12v電壓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此你需要串聯至少5個2.7v cap當一條電池。<br />\n最簡單的保護方式是並聯一個12v齊納二極管。這個當時並不十分穩固，可以話係，只堪一用。而且買齊納二極管需要注意額定值達到4w比較好。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"好嘅大約都明<br />\n<br />\n我補充一下<br />\n<br />\n因為我依架充電唔會充好耐,大約2分鐘就會停之後就放電,所以cap嘅電壓就唔洗咁高<br />\n<br />\n要嘅能量都只係e=vit/2=144j <br />\n<br />\n咁嘅情況下我應該係推高電壓同太陽能板一樣<br />\n<br />\n定係計到電壓只係比摩打高少少,然後推高容量?<br />\n<br />\n之後有無話cap可存能量同輸入能量差唔多會充得有效率啲?<br />\n<br />\n唔太識解釋我想問嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry for 1999"},{"pid":"661ea3e3a5faeb7d1fc4831b7397934da509046a","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"260c30237340855538136a77d195060ade039d39","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:58:56.000Z","msg":"最好再並聯一個0.25瓦 的100k歐姆電阻都會是比較理想的做法"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:02:06.000Z","msg":"為何?"},{"pid":"1322296edc67cbd89eb53deb7ee55516da14177b","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661ea3e3