0Z","msg":"兩個都係2.7v<br />\n使用唔建議超過2.5v<br />\n可以考慮5或6個串聯"},{"pid":"aacbe6174f113c2aec9659fed6fcca0e6b201a6a","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4933db196b7cedbd47632470b411d35ca198974","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bf33d4cdb9c58463acf852201edff5c0309e031","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56a8ecd5535e70eb73997084a232aef50a8b2b5f","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:49:18.000Z","msg":"電池都會過充<br />\n所以會有過壓保護<br />\n鋰電（磷酸鐵鋰除外）過4.2就會危險著火爆炸<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n太陽能板係一個電流源<br />\n它本身由太陽能電池組成。<br />\n你那個它可以提供從1v到20v的電壓<br />\n因此實際可以提供超過12v電壓。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因此你需要串聯至少5個2.7v cap當一條電池。<br />\n最簡單的保護方式是並聯一個12v齊納二極管。這個當時並不十分穩固，可以話係，只堪一用。而且買齊納二極管需要注意額定值達到4w比較好。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"好嘅大約都明<br />\n<br />\n我補充一下<br />\n<br />\n因為我依架充電唔會充好耐,大約2分鐘就會停之後就放電,所以cap嘅電壓就唔洗咁高<br />\n<br />\n要嘅能量都只係e=vit/2=144j <br />\n<br />\n咁嘅情況下我應該係推高電壓同太陽能板一樣<br />\n<br />\n定係計到電壓只係比摩打高少少,然後推高容量?<br />\n<br />\n之後有無話cap可存能量同輸入能量差唔多會充得有效率啲?<br />\n<br />\n唔太識解釋我想問嘅野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />sorry for 1999"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:15:14.000Z","msg":"第一，vit點解要除2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二，唔建議俾太高電壓落摩打<br />\n可能可以用但唔建議。可能會導致過負荷，燒壞。 應該跟摩打電壓。<br />\n<br />\n是，容量可以無限推高。但是隨著並聯sc或者話ultra capacitor數量的增加，不平衡問題可能就會出現，而且充電時間也會增加。<br />\n<br />\n第四，sc效率高的<br />\n<br />\n第五，建議並聯2個9v led<br />\n如果過壓起碼有燈仔顯示。<br />\n建議串聯一個電阻限流。<br />\n以一個普通led計可能係10毫安<br />\n咁電阻就係齊納二極管的保護電壓<br />\n15/(R+9/0.01)*R=3<br />\nR=200左右大概，你自己計同試下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:40:55.000Z","msg":"1.我都唔知 當時做嗰個係咁計 但係又岩 我唔記得左個解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.當cpu咁oc<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身都試過比多電壓<br />\n<br />\n3.簡單嚟講決定完電壓之後容量有幾細整幾細?在用塊12v太陽能板0.2a充兩分鐘嘅情況下<br />\n<br />\n4.sc指咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.用開tat錶(萬用錶)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a68bb8b3f6ebf953951e1965d3c5750d9f747d6","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dac89f1ba70b6f4de57056f7f082e0ab55b05fe","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e6a88a2e5fbf93283d28667c77d6e1bdd92df2","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22fb9a86e0095b7e28751aa2c8c8a0c2d0179093","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:16:50.000Z","msg":"rs no.幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:35:08.000Z","msg":"之前用果隻5f同10f<br />\n7637757<br />\n7637769"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:38:06.000Z","msg":"兩個都係2.7v<br />\n使用唔建議超過2.5v<br />\n可以考慮5或6個串聯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:43:07.000Z","msg":"如果好似我張圖咁砌正常full-load 應該係4v<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係又好神奇地充到5.5~5.8v<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97e4578b936e6a668ddf9dd9609a6cd1a02d39ca","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a68bb8b3f6ebf953951e1965d3c5750d9f747d6","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dac89f1ba70b6f4de57056f7f082e0ab55b05fe","tid":2264482,"uid":242102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4e6a88a2e5fbf93283d28667c77d6e1bdd92df2","tid":2264482,"uid":367351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T17:35